{"tid":1444242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回到 721","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T11:42:43.000Z","uid":213889,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f4b828d641a1cf004000bfdcd0e2651b5c8119","tid":1444242,"uid":213889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:52:45.000Z","msg":"由6月到依家 每一日都不停有唔同既新聞更新<br />\n一次又一次既催淚彈放題 一次又一次無差別咁拉人<br />\n班狗仔每一件既英勇事蹟都多到數唔哂<br />\n去過夢境既每一位 相信大家都慢慢開始習慣 都唔會覺得陌生<br />\n警犬最近仲開多左記招 嘗試從各方面分散大家既注意<br />\n<br />\n直到依家相信大家都唔會忘記721發生咩事<br />\n不如就回憶一下個晚發生過啲咩事⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>上環</strong></span></ins><br />\n1. 警察亦在<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有警告情況下，發射36發橡膠子彈，每一槍都瞄準示威者身體的重要器官</span>，導致多名示威者中槍受傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aG8KtQR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaG8KtQR.jpg&h=ee561749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>元朗</strong></span></ins><br />\n1. 白衣人於晚上在元朗港鐵站，甚至衝上月台及衝入車廂<span style=\"color: red;\">無差別地狂毆市民</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">兩名當值軍裝警員見到事件發生卻往反方向離開</span>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">警方被質疑與黑社會合謀</span></strong>，縱容惡勢力毆打市民<br />\n<br />\n2. 多名白衣人到處狂毆途人，甚至有<span style=\"color: red;\">老人及孕婦被毆打至昏迷倒在地上</span>，亦有<span style=\"color: red;\">立法會議員及記者被打至頭破血流</span><br />\n<br />\n3.  有市民於危急關頭報警求助，但<span style=\"color: red;\">撥打999求助熱線卻被cut線</span>及有指得到回應：<span style=\"color: red;\">「驚咪唔好出街囉」</span>，更有<span style=\"color: red;\">警署警閘不讓市民報案</span>，市民求助無援<br />\n<br />\n4. 白衣人於約晚上8時半開始慢慢聚集於鳳攸北街，各人手持藤條等，有附近商户指突然<span style=\"color: red;\">有數百人聚集，但一直沒看到警方到場了解</span><br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">立法會議員何君堯到元朗雞地與大批白衣人握手，更舉姆指及鼓掌稱讚</span>，有白衣人向何君堯稱「你地係我既英雄」。有人認出其中一名與何議員握手的白衣人正是元朗站內狂毆市民的白衣人<br />\n<br />\n6. 元朗站襲擊事件後，有警方深夜出動大批防暴警到南邊圍村，當時村內有大批白衣人手持鐵通及木棍，但<span style=\"color: red;\">警方並沒有拘捕任何人</span>，並在記者訪問時指出<span style=\"color: red;\">「白衣既人並唔等於有分參與打鬥」「刑事科同事落到黎係唔見有任何人揸住攻擊性武器既，呢樣野的要好明確話比你地聽」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/We2vpnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWe2vpnL.jpg&h=f6fb84ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6iiuEV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6iiuEV5.jpg&h=01b46a45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hOQAAur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhOQAAur.jpg&h=e5e6cdfc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfawTf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnfawTf7.jpg&h=c88e889d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cN2Ldf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcN2Ldf7.jpg&h=be54a6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hUu5XHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhUu5XHO.jpg&h=247f07fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jzFT6A9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjzFT6A9.jpg&h=aa40ea13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖：反送中 文宣<br />\n<br />\n班狗做過咩 大家都清楚 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>煲翻大721啦！用最大火煲阿！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑社會完 依家就到福建佬 可恥！</strong></span><br />\n我地目標要明確 除左夢遊撚狗外<br />\n我地仍然要記住<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一、徹底撤回逃犯修例<br />\n二、撤回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，撤查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n五、全面落實雙普選</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>兄弟爬山 各自努力 不撤不散<br />\n不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆 核彈炸落黎都不割</strong></div><br />\n革命係漫長 身邊雖然係陌生人 但亦都係同路人<br />\n希望終有一日 各位可以除低口罩 除低身上既gear相見<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span></div><br />\n有咩甩漏 希望大家幫手補番 屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948cf12e941c02b58a7563dffd1294cf326b57a4","tid":1444242,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"721元朗<br />\n811北角尖沙咀"},{"pid":"9c41e5d2e94ac875f166855128cc7e5cbfc95e04","tid":1444242,"uid":104965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"721 依然無道歉同回應<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法迫特首為721 道歉"},{"pid":"8b94e6c28f493b14835fce21c6e9bfd462264d22","tid":1444242,"uid":213889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c41e5d2e94ac875f166855128cc7e5cbfc95e04","tid":1444242,"uid":104965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"721 依然無道歉同回應<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法迫特首為721 道歉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:55:52.000Z","msg":"班狗官依家打民生牌 好驚有一部份人覺得：政府有做野，就收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9bc5af245d4d5e6d49771fbba92881d273ddb3","tid":1444242,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b94e6c28f493b14835fce21c6e9bfd462264d22","tid":1444242,"uid":213889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c41e5d2e94ac875f166855128cc7e5cbfc95e04","tid":1444242,"uid":104965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"721 依然無道歉同回應<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法迫特首為721 道歉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:55:52.000Z","msg":"班狗官依家打民生牌 好驚有一部份人覺得：政府有做野，就收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:57:22.000Z","msg":"721 係無妥協餘地<br />\n<br />\n民生牌每人派10萬都唔可以改變呢個黑暗事實"},{"pid":"d1652f0a290a892865dea02eec8542a27b45ddcb","tid":1444242,"uid":213889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:02:36.000Z","msg":"自推100"},{"pid":"c79f8a9a73d5430fafd65f6dc7e2a1e5a45e6ea9","tid":1444242,"uid":78962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:03:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4926b5acf69b737327b78045d87fd9deb5b78e4f","tid":1444242,"uid":262261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:08:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e47d30560a0773a78ac14f24b935be442174d5de","tid":1444242,"uid":213889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"自推200"},{"pid":"95731dfbf3eed69900edbe91259184fc40911574","tid":1444242,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:37:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"fa860b503df8118919307381d873d163a9aebbbd","tid":1444242,"uid":178791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"05d55b721a9e53379ff89559258948b4071cd4b2","tid":1444242,"uid":301479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:52:28.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲 </span></span></div><br />\n黑社會無差別襲擊人, 警方唔拉黑社會<br />\n警黑合作, 警署落閘, 999唔通,  無人落charge<br />\n<br />\n721元朗恐襲第22日: 無人落charge, 無警停職<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 不分化 不割席<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 香港警方=黑社會, 香港警方=恐怖主義組織<br />\n無忘721<br />\n記者請日日問</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"1325aed711b2fdd489a6216ff9df5390fc0f2b84","tid":1444242,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:52:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲 </span></span></div><br />\n黑社會無差別襲擊人, 警方唔拉黑社會<br />\n警黑合作, 警署落閘, 999唔通,  無人落charge<br />\n<br />\n721元朗恐襲第22日: 無人落charge, 無警停職<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 不分化 不割席<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 香港警方=黑社會, 香港警方=恐怖主義組織<br />\n無忘721<br />\n記者請日日問</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"9262e97ca7f6613de3f15b07233d834bb76334ad","tid":1444242,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"4ea1ed983588ce999f3b73402e1fa74f5fc58900","tid":1444242,"uid":213889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:53:30.000Z","msg":"再輕輕推一推"},{"pid":"c3077f281b1beaa1b72853c4f218d0612de9ad68","tid":1444242,"uid":213889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:42:11.000Z","msg":"推一推先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5057c335e4337c016f71ef002200b9f6ab0132bf","tid":1444242,"uid":213889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}